messages.message: :alarm: <!here> Note that PreProd Jenkins is currently *DOWN* - All Github operations are likely to fail.

Troubleshooting thread for context. I don't recall how to start an incident channel.
https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C035SLYCJ9X/p1737656399021889
you can open the three dots menu and choose "Aegis create incident"

:yellow_circle: PreProd is back online, but I'm not yet convinced it's stable.
Will monitor and update as needed.
:alarm: PreProd is *NOT* stable yet. The upgrade has caused some manner of incompatibility with the builder AMIs, looking into it now.

:white_check_mark: PreProd Jenkins should be back up and working correctly.

Note that there is a HUGE backlog of stuff that's likely to kick off now, so it might be a little choppy while things naturally jitter themselves back into a semblance of amortized CPU time, but it shouldn't tip over again... hopefully.
